NK015(ba)024:0: tshogs 'dod yon lam khyer bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)024:2: tshogs kyi gtso bo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)024:3: tshogs kyi mchod pa lag len du bya ba la don drug ste /
NK015(ba)024:4: sngon du bya ba'i rim pa dang /
NK015(ba)024:6: mtshams bcad cing dkyil 'khor sprul pa dang /
NK015(ba)024:7: tshogs byin gyis brlabs shing gzi byin dbab pa dang /
NK015(ba)024:8: mchod cing rol ba'i cho ga dang /
NK015(ba)024:9: bkra shis brjod cing lhag ma'i las bya ba'o //
NK015(ba)024:10: dang po sngon du bya ba'i rim pa ni /
NK015(ba)024:11: dus khyad par can la nyi ma thal phyin chad bya ste /
NK015(ba)024:13: de nas man+dala ci rigs pa byi dor byas la /
NK015(ba)024:14: lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i tshom bu bkram /
NK015(ba)024:21: gzhan yang tshogs kyi zhal zas ni /
NK015(ba)024:22: dza gad pany+tsa sbyar ba yang /
NK015(ba)024:23: dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs su bzhag go //
NK015(ba)024:24: sha'i rigs thams cad lho phyogs su bzhag /
NK015(ba)024:25: shing thog dang zho phrum la sogs rnams ni shar du bzhag /
NK015(ba)024:26: zla ba rdzogs ni tshogs bshos la zla gam bya ba byang phyogs su bzhag go //
NK015(ba)024:27: de dag thams cad la dar mthing gi zhal kheb bya la mi mngon par bya'o //
NK015(ba)024:28: gzhan yang bris sku dang rten rnams bkram mo //
NK015(ba)024:29: dam tshig dang ldan pa ma rtogs pa'i mi mi bsnyon /
NK015(ba)024:30: de nas yon bdag la sogs pa thams cad gang zhu bar 'dod pa thams cad kyis /
NK015(ba)024:31: sdig pa bshags pa'i cho ga bya /
NK015(ba)024:32: de nas don gnyis pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK015(ba)024:33: yon bdag la sogs pa thams cad kyis /
NK015(ba)024:35: slob bu'i phyag 'tshal zhing 'di skad do //
NK015(ba)024:37: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dbyer med pa'i thugs ka nas /
NK015(ba)024:38: h'u dkar ser dmar ljang bzhi spros pa las /
NK015(ba)024:39: shar sgor rgyas 'debs ma dkar mo /
NK015(ba)024:40: lho dam pa ma ser mo /
NK015(ba)024:41: nub tu zab mo dmar mo /
NK015(ba)024:42: byang du tshe 'phel ma ljang ku bzhis thal mo sbyar nas zhu bar bsgom ma /
NK015(ba)024:43: kye rdo rje slob dpon dpal dang ldan //
NK015(ba)024:44: srid pa'i sdug bsngal bcad pa dang //
NK015(ba)024:45: byis pa'i lam las brgal ba'i phyir //
NK015(ba)024:46: spyod pa'i khyad par mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)024:47: phyogs bcu dus bzhi bsam yas kyis //
NK015(ba)024:48: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad dang //
NK015(ba)024:49: sras kyi tshogs 'dus ji snyed pa //
NK015(ba)024:50: spyod pa'i khyad par 'di las byung //
NK015(ba)024:51: de bas bde ba chen po yi //
NK015(ba)024:52: ngo mtshar yang dag bstan du gsol //
NK015(ba)024:53: byang chub snying po mchog gi bar //
NK015(ba)024:54: bde mchog spyod pa yang dag blang //
NK015(ba)024:55: zhes gsol ba lan gsum gdab pa'o //
NK015(ba)024:56: de nas bzhes par gnang la /
NK015(ba)024:57: rdo rje slob dpon nas bzung ste /
NK015(ba)024:58: thams cad kyi dbu la me tog phreng ba gdags so //
NK015(ba)024:59: spyi don gsum pa mtshams bcad cing /
NK015(ba)024:61: rdo rje slob dpon nas brtsam ste rnal 'byor pa
NK015(ba)024:62: thams cad gzhung lugs gang mang rung ba'i ngos nas
NK015(ba)024:65: ting nge 'dzin rim pa bzhi dang /
NK015(ba)024:66: cho 'phrul bzhis dal gyi dkyil 'khor sprul /
NK015(ba)024:67: spyan 'dren pa nas mchod cing bsnyen pa'i bar du so so'i gzhung bzhin du bagyi'o //
NK015(ba)024:68: spyi don bzhi pa tshogs kyis mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK015(ba)024:69: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la pha h'u phata /
NK015(ba)024:70: zhi khro gang yin rang gi snying po brjod la gsal gdab /
NK015(ba)024:71: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham gsum spros pa las /
NK015(ba)024:72: tshogs kyi zhal zas bsreg sbyangs bkru bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)024:73: khams gsum gyi chos thams cad la yang de bzhin bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)024:75: gtor ma'i steng 'dod yon gyi lha mo /
NK015(ba)024:77: 'og dug gsum sha khrag gi rus pa'i mchod pa byin gyis rlabs /
NK015(ba)024:78: dza gad ni gong sman gyi byin gyis rlabs pa bzhin no //
NK015(ba)024:79: de nas tshogs zhing spyan drang ba ni /
NK015(ba)024:80: badz+ra sa man dza h'u dza /
NK015(ba)024:82: mdun gyis nam mkhar dbus su phur pa'i lha tshogs /
NK015(ba)024:83: g.yas su zhi ba'i lha tshogs /
NK015(ba)024:84: g.yon du khro bo'i lha tshogs /
NK015(ba)024:85: gtso bo'i dbu la slob dpon pad+ma rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams dang /
NK015(ba)024:86: 'og gi cha la chos skyong ma mgon la sogs pa rnams bsgom la /
NK015(ba)024:87: de nas tshogs gzi byin bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)024:88: rdo rje dril bu bzung nas dbyangs dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK015(ba)024:90: 'byung ba chen po nam mkha' ni /
NK015(ba)024:92: / 'byung ba chen po lnga pa ste //
NK015(ba)024:96: 'dod pa'i mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK015(ba)024:97: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)024:98: de nas kun bzang mchod pa la bzhi /
NK015(ba)024:99: phyi kun bzang gi mchod pa /
NK015(ba)024:100: nang kun bzang gis mchod pa /
NK015(ba)024:102: de kho na nyid kun bzang gi mchod pa'i dmigs pa ni gong bzhin du bya'o //
NK015(ba)024:103: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK015(ba)024:104: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyis //
NK015(ba)024:105: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas pa //
NK015(ba)024:106: spyod pa rgya mtsho rmad byung kun //
NK015(ba)024:107: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK015(ba)024:108: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo b+hi shwa mu khe b+h+ya /
NK015(ba)024:109: sarba tad khang ud g+ha te s+pha ra na hi mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)024:110: de nas rmad byung gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)024:111: gzugs kyi lha mo dkar mo phyag na me long bsnams pa spyan la /
NK015(ba)024:112: sgra'i lha mo sngon mo phag na pi wam 'dzin pa snyan la /
NK015(ba)024:113: dri'i lha mo ser mo phyag na spos bsnams pa shangs la /
NK015(ba)024:114: ro'i lha mo dmar po phyag na zhal zas ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa bsnams pas lce la /
NK015(ba)024:115: ro mchog lha mo ljang ku phyag na na baza'i
NK015(ba)024:116: gang ba rdo rjes mtshan pa bsnams pas sku la
NK015(ba)024:117: / chos kyi lha mo mthing ka phyag na chos
NK015(ba)024:118: 'byung gru gsum bsnams pa thugs kar thim par bsgom
NK015(ba)024:119: / la / h'u gzugs ni lag gnyis me long 'dzin //
NK015(ba)024:120: gzugs mdzes spyod pas phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK015(ba)024:121: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK015(ba)024:122: gzugs kyi lha mo spyan la thim //
NK015(ba)024:124: h'u sgra ni lag gnyis pi wam btegs //
NK015(ba)024:125: bde ba'i sgra snyan phyogs bcur sgrogs //
NK015(ba)024:126: dbyangs snyan yid 'phrog glu dbyangs len //
NK015(ba)024:127: sgra'i lha mo snyan la thim //
NK015(ba)024:129: h'u dri ni lag gnyis spos bsnam ste //
NK015(ba)024:130: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa 'phro //
NK015(ba)024:131: kun tu tshim byed dri bsung ldan //
NK015(ba)024:132: dri'i lha mo shangs la thim //
NK015(ba)024:134: ro ni lag gnyis snod bsnam ste //
NK015(ba)024:135: bcud ldan ro mchog lnga brgyar spro //
NK015(ba)024:136: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK015(ba)024:137: ro'i lha mo ljags la thim //
NK015(ba)024:139: reg ni rdo rje yang 'khyud ma //
NK015(ba)024:140: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK015(ba)024:141: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK015(ba)024:142: reg gi lha mo sku la 'khril //
NK015(ba)024:145: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i sku //
NK015(ba)024:146: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK015(ba)024:147: chos kyi lha mo thugs kar thim //
NK015(ba)024:148: badz+ra d+har+m+aa d+ha d+hu badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)024:149: gtor ma'i bar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur par bsgom la /
NK015(ba)024:150: lha tshogs rnams kyi ljags rdo rje'i sbu gur gyur nas /
NK015(ba)024:151: chu la nyi zer phog pa bzhin du gsol bar bsgom /
NK015(ba)024:152: gtor ma'i 'og tu dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i phung por gyur pa /
NK015(ba)024:153: khyad par khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams mnyes par bsam la /
NK015(ba)024:154: rdo rje zhing chen dri ni ngad dpung dpung //
NK015(ba)024:155: rak+ta rgya mtsho'i tshogs ni ci li li //
NK015(ba)024:156: kem rus mang po'i tshogs ni khra la la //
NK015(ba)024:157: mang sa gal chen tshogs ni thang mar bdal /
NK015(ba)024:159: / 'di ltar dug gsum mchod pa bshams lags kyis //
NK015(ba)024:160: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK015(ba)024:161: bcom ldan dpal chen khrag 'thung he ru ka /
NK015(ba)024:162: sangs rgyas zhing la nyon mongs sgrol mdzad cing /
NK015(ba)024:164: / 'gro ba'i don la yid bzhin skur ston pa'i //
NK015(ba)024:165: tshogs rje rngam pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK015(ba)024:166: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs chen mang po rnams //
NK015(ba)024:167: keng rus tshogs la bstod pa'i tshul ston cing //
NK015(ba)024:168: log 'dren gdug pa'i bdud dpung 'joms mdzad pa'i //
NK015(ba)024:169: rgyug pa'i stobs chen pho nya mang po'i tshogs //
NK015(ba)024:170: dug gsum rgya mtsho'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK015(ba)024:171: spyi don lnga pa mchod cing rol ba ni /
NK015(ba)024:172: gong gis lha mo bzhis zhu ba byed par bsgom la /
NK015(ba)024:173: phyag tshang bas tshogs rdzas btegs la 'di skad do //
NK015(ba)024:175: gzigs shig mdzes ldan dam pa'i chos /
NK015(ba)024:177: / 'di la rnam rtog bya mi rung //
NK015(ba)024:178: bram ze khyi dang gdol pa gsum //
NK015(ba)024:179: rang bzhin gcig pa nyid du rol //
NK015(ba)024:180: gnyis pa tshogs la rol ba'i zhu ba ni /
NK015(ba)024:181: tshogs kyi gtso bo rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs lha tshogs rnams kyis /
NK015(ba)024:185: snyan gyis gsan par bsam la /
NK015(ba)024:186: rdo rje 'dzin sogs dgongs su gsol //
NK015(ba)024:187: bdag gi tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK015(ba)024:188: mnyes pa'i don du bstabs lags na //
NK015(ba)024:189: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK015(ba)024:190: slob dpon gyis lan gdab pa la gsum gyi dang po /
NK015(ba)024:191: tshogs gnyis 'di 'dod yon ye shes don la mnyes pa ni /
NK015(ba)024:192: tshogs gnyis dbyer med ye shes chen pos /
NK015(ba)024:193: nyon mongs rang rgyud pa bsregs par bsam la /
NK015(ba)024:194: ye shes chen po las byung ba'i //
NK015(ba)024:195: tshogs chen 'bar bas nyon mongs bsregs //
NK015(ba)024:196: de 'dra'i bde ba thob nas kyang //
NK015(ba)024:197: kun gyis a ho su kha brjod //
NK015(ba)024:200: gnyis pa tshogs kyi rang bzhin sku gsum du bstan pa ni /
NK015(ba)024:201: stong nyid zab mo'i don la 'byor pa'i sangs rgyas bde mchog chos sku /
NK015(ba)024:203: bde bar mdzad pa longs sku ste sku gsum dbyer med rdo rje sems dpa' nyid /
NK015(ba)024:204: stong la 'byor pa'i rtags su dam pa 'byung //
NK015(ba)024:205: bde mchog bde mdzad bde bar mdzad pa ste //
NK015(ba)024:206: rig pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' nyid //
NK015(ba)024:207: de ni byang chub sems su rig pas rig /
NK015(ba)024:208: gsum pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin bstan pa ni /
NK015(ba)024:209: bya ba stong pa'i rang bzhin /
NK015(ba)024:210: chub pa snang ba'i rang bzhin /
NK015(ba)024:211: sems dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK015(ba)024:212: snang stong gnyis med kyi don rtogs na dngos grub kyi mchog go //
NK015(ba)024:213: byang chub sems ni dngos grub mchog /
NK015(ba)024:214: der rig yang dag nyid ces bya /
NK015(ba)024:216: / 'od dang mngon shes mnga' la sogs //
NK015(ba)024:217: ldan yang gnod sbyin chos mi shes //
NK015(ba)024:218: gsum pa yo byad lam du khyer nas 'dod yon tshogs su bstab pa la gsum ste /
NK015(ba)024:219: dang po bgo ba bza' ba'i yo byad ni /
NK015(ba)024:220: stong nyid zab mo'i don rnal ma la /
NK015(ba)024:221: rang rig pa'i blo 'byor pa ni rnal 'byor ro //
NK015(ba)024:223: na bza' dang ni zhal zas rnams //
NK015(ba)024:224: bsgrub pa'i rdzas su dbang bsgyur te //
NK015(ba)024:225: gsol na dngos grub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK015(ba)024:226: gnyis pa glu tshig sgra'i yo byad ni /
NK015(ba)024:227: ma 'gags ma dmigs grags stong dbyer med kyi ngang
NK015(ba)024:228: nas glu dbyangs tshig bcad bsgrags na dngos grub kyi
NK015(ba)024:229: mchog go // rnal 'byor rig 'dzin dam ldan pas //
NK015(ba)024:230: glu dang tshig gi sgra rnams ni //
NK015(ba)024:231: gsung gi ngo bor byin rlabs nas //
NK015(ba)024:232: bsgrag na dngos grub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK015(ba)024:233: gsum pa bro gar 'du 'phro'i yo byad ni /
NK015(ba)024:234: lha rtog dbyer med kyi ngang nas /
NK015(ba)024:235: 'od zer 'phros khams gsum sems can thams cad la phog /
NK015(ba)024:236: yi dam lha yab yum gyi skur gyur /
NK015(ba)024:237: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad la phog thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK015(ba)024:238: tshur 'dus dngos grub rnam gsum ster bar bsgom /
NK015(ba)024:240: bro dang gar gyi mchod byas te /
NK015(ba)024:243: dngos grub mchog kyang thob par 'gyur //
NK015(ba)024:247: sngar gyi gsang ba'i lha mo bzhis zhu bar bsam la 'di skad do //
NK015(ba)024:248: h'u mdzad h'u gi thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK015(ba)024:249: lcang lo bcas pa'i pad+ma b+han+d+ha ru //
NK015(ba)024:250: tshe 'dzin mchog gi dmar chen dam pas bskang //
NK015(ba)024:251: pad+ma zil tig dri dang rak+ta kha //
NK015(ba)024:252: rdo rje las kyi chu dang pany+tsa a mri ta //
NK015(ba)024:253: sha chen mkha' lding shel sgong gzugs kyi tshogs la sogs //
NK015(ba)024:254: sman chen lnga dang tshe dang byi la se //
NK015(ba)024:255: sbyor dang sgrol ba'i bdud rtsi mchog nyid kyis //
NK015(ba)024:256: h'u mdzad h'u gis thugs dam bskangs bar mdzod //
NK015(ba)024:257: ces pad+ma'i phyag rgyas len par bya'o //
NK015(ba)024:263: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i chu 'di ni //
NK015(ba)024:264: ye shes lha la phul ba'i tshe //
NK015(ba)024:265: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad mnyes //
NK015(ba)024:266: rig 'dzin rnams la phul ba'i tshe //
NK015(ba)024:267: dngos grub rgya mtsho thams cad ster //
NK015(ba)024:268: dam can srung ma mchod pa'i tshe //
NK015(ba)024:269: srung ma rnams kyi thugs dam bskangs //
NK015(ba)024:270: rnal 'byor bdag gis myong ba'i tshe //
NK015(ba)024:271: dbang dang dngos grub yongs su rdzogs //
NK015(ba)024:272: bdud dang bgegs la phog pa'i tshe //
NK015(ba)024:273: lus sems thal ba'i rdul du brlag /
NK015(ba)024:276: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK015(ba)024:278: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)024:279: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
NK015(ba)024:280: sman mchod dngos la bzhi'i dang po rig 'dzin la 'bul ba ni /
NK015(ba)024:281: lha mo rnams kyang nyi zla'i skyog zhal thogs nas
NK015(ba)024:282: bdud rtsi rig 'dzin rnams la phul bar bsgom la
NK015(ba)024:283: / chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK015(ba)024:284: bka' brgyud bla ma rje btsun la //
NK015(ba)024:285: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK015(ba)024:286: thugs rje brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)024:287: na mahsarba ta tha ga ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
NK015(ba)024:288: dug lnga ma spangs dug gsum rnam dag pa'i //
NK015(ba)024:289: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK015(ba)024:290: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK015(ba)024:291: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)024:292: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
NK015(ba)024:293: bka' brgyud bla ma u rgyan yab yum rig 'dzin
NK015(ba)024:294: yab yum sras 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal
NK015(ba)024:295: du sarba pany+tsa a mri ta la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)024:296: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyu mnyes shing tshims par mdzad du gsol /
NK015(ba)024:297: bdag cag rnams la mchog thun mong gi dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK015(ba)024:298: gnyis pa yi dam la 'bul ba la gsum gyi dang po zhi ba ni /
NK015(ba)024:299: ho rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyis //
NK015(ba)024:300: srid pa'i sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa'i //
NK015(ba)024:301: bde chen kun bzang yab yum la //
NK015(ba)024:302: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK015(ba)024:303: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)024:304: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
NK015(ba)024:305: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga //
NK015(ba)024:306: ye shes dbyings su rnam dag pa'i //
NK015(ba)024:307: rig lnga bde gshegs yab yum la //
NK015(ba)024:308: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK015(ba)024:309: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)024:310: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
NK015(ba)024:311: rnam shes tshogs dang spyod yul rnams //
NK015(ba)024:312: byang chub sems su rnam dag pa'i //
NK015(ba)024:313: sems dpa' lcam dral tshogs rnams la //
NK015(ba)024:314: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK015(ba)024:315: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)024:316: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
NK015(ba)024:317: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK015(ba)024:319: / 'gro drug dbyings su sbyor mdzad pa'i //
NK015(ba)024:320: sprul pa'i thub pa drug rnams la //
NK015(ba)024:321: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK015(ba)024:322: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)024:323: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
NK015(ba)024:324: phyi nang bdud tshogs thams cad 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK015(ba)024:325: gnas yul ro lang rdo rje bcing sdom 'beb //
NK015(ba)024:326: sprul pa sgo skyong khro rgyal yab yum la //
NK015(ba)024:327: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK015(ba)024:328: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)024:329: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
